      "text": "on the statement of cash flows."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 282440.0,
      "end_time": 285410.0,
      "text": "The answer is not B, investing activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 285410.0,
      "end_time": 287960.0,
      "text": "Debt is never part of investments."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 287960.0,
      "end_time": 290210.0,
      "text": "The answer is not C either."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 290210.0,
      "end_time": 292790.0,
      "text": "Even though debt is part of financing activities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 292790.0,
      "end_time": 295250.0,
      "text": "interest paid on debt is on the income statement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 295250.0,
      "end_time": 296360.0,
      "text": "as an expense."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 296360.0,
      "end_time": 298910.0,
      "text": "An income statement is the accrual accounting view"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 298910.0,
      "end_time": 300680.0,
      "text": "of the operating activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 300680.0,
      "end_time": 304130.0,
      "text": "ASPE requires that it remain as part of operating activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 304130.0,
      "end_time": 307100.0,
      "text": "The answer is therefore A, an operating activity."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 307100.0,
      "end_time": 309140.0,
      "text": "An in-depth explanation of this will"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 309140.0,
      "end_time": 311321.0,
      "text": "be provided in a future video."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 311321.0,
      "end_time": 313070.0,
      "text": "Now that we understand the activities that"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 313070.0,
      "end_time": 314569.0,
      "text": "make up the statement of cash flows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 314569.0,
      "end_time": 316310.0,
      "text": "we can look at an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 316310.0,
      "end_time": 317810.0,
      "text": "Note that this statement is so large"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 317810.0,
      "end_time": 319560.0,
