    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 321650.0,
      "end_time": 324080.0,
      "text": "But the statement is actually one statement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 324080.0,
      "end_time": 327042.0,
      "text": "with the three activities listed immediately after each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 327042.0,
      "end_time": 329000.0,
