    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 340380.0,
      "end_time": 342169.0,
      "text": "and the period of time covered."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 342169.0,
      "end_time": 344460.0,
      "text": "Note, similar to the income statement and the statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 344460.0,
      "end_time": 346260.0,
      "text": "of retained earnings, this statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 346260.0,
      "end_time": 350037.0,
      "text": "is for a period of time, most commonly one year."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 350037.0,
      "end_time": 352120.0,
      "text": "The statement opens with the heading for operating"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 352120.0,
      "end_time": 354280.0,
      "text": "activities and then starts with net income"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 354280.0,
      "end_time": 356260.0,
      "text": "from the income statement."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 356260.0,
      "end_time": 358120.0,
      "text": "All the other amounts are reconciling"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 358120.0,
      "end_time": 360910.0,
      "text": "items between net income from the income statement, which,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 360910.0,
      "end_time": 362860.0,
      "text": "remember, uses accrual accounting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 362860.0,
      "end_time": 364720.0,
      "text": "and the cash flow from operations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 364720.0,
      "end_time": 366670.0,
      "text": "which uses cash accounting."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 366670.0,
      "end_time": 369670.0,
      "text": "These items are known as non-cash items."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 369670.0,
      "end_time": 372580.0,
      "text": "This includes things such as depreciation and the change"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 372580.0,
      "end_time": 374500.0,
      "text": "in current assets and liability accounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 374500.0,
      "end_time": 375940.0,
      "text": "from the balance sheet."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 375940.0,
      "end_time": 378940.0,
      "text": "Again, an in-depth explanation of these adjustments"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 378940.0,
      "end_time": 380770.0,
      "text": "will be made in a future video."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 380770.0,
      "end_time": 382900.0,
      "text": "For now, what&#39;s important is to simply understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 382900.0,
      "end_time": 384790.0,
      "text": "the structure of the statement and why"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 384790.0,
      "end_time": 387040.0,
      "text": "it is required under ASPE."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 387040.0,
      "end_time": 388420.0,
      "text": "At the bottom of this section, we"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 388420.0,
      "end_time": 391180.0,
      "text": "see that operating activities resulted in a net cash"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 391180.0,
      "end_time": 394540.0,
      "text": "inflow of $21,400."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 394540.0,
      "end_time": 396400.0,
      "text": "Investing activities are next."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 396400.0,
      "end_time": 398320.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll note there&#39;s a net cash outflow"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 398320.0,
      "end_time": 403030.0,
      "text": "of $7,500 due to the purchase of both equipment and investments."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 403030.0,
      "end_time": 404830.0,
      "text": "A cash outflow from investing activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 404830.0,
      "end_time": 408040.0,
      "text": "is not unusual, because it means that the business is investing"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 408040.0,
      "end_time": 410830.0,
      "text": "in the future ability to generate revenue."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 410830.0,
      "end_time": 414340.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s a positive thing for investors and creditors."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 414340.0,
      "end_time": 416857.0,
      "text": "Finally, let&#39;s look at the financing activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 416857.0,
      "end_time": 418690.0,
      "text": "Here, we see that the owners of the business"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 418690.0,
      "end_time": 420670.0,
      "text": "contributed more cash to the business"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 420670.0,
      "end_time": 423184.0,
      "text": "and that the business paid down some of their debt."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 423184.0,
      "end_time": 425350.0,
      "text": "We can also see that the business paid out dividends"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 425350.0,
      "end_time": 426520.0,
      "text": "to the owners."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 426520.0,
      "end_time": 430000.0,
      "text": "This ties into the $2,500 we saw in the statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 430000.0,
      "end_time": 433600.0,
      "text": "of retained earnings as a dividend paid during the year."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 433600.0,
      "end_time": 437639.0,
      "text": "A subtotal of the financing activities is then seen."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 437639.0,
      "end_time": 439180.0,
      "text": "The bottom of the cash flow statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 439180.0,
      "end_time": 441130.0,
      "text": "shows the net change in cash."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 441130.0,
      "end_time": 443210.0,
      "text": "How is this calculated?"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 443210.0,
      "end_time": 445930.0,
      "text": "This is a summation of all three activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 445930.0,
      "end_time": 448240.0,
      "text": "For this cash flow, that would be the operating inflow"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 448240.0,
      "end_time": 453010.0,
      "text": "of 21,400, investing and financing outflows of 7,500"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 453010.0,
      "end_time": 455630.0,
      "text": "and 1,700, respectively."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 455630.0,
      "end_time": 457960.0,
      "text": "This results in a change in cash during the year"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 457960.0,
      "end_time": 461800.0,
      "text": "of $12,200, an inflow."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 461800.0,
      "end_time": 464970.0,
      "text": "This amount is noted on the cash flow statement."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 464970.0,
      "end_time": 469220.0,
      "text": "We then add this to the beginning balance of 72,300,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 469220.0,
      "end_time": 472070.0,
      "text": "which we obtain from the prior year&#39;s balance sheet."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 472070.0,
      "end_time": 474260.0,
      "text": "Remember that the closing cash from one period"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 474260.0,
      "end_time": 477610.0,
      "text": "becomes the opening balance for the next period."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 477610.0,
      "end_time": 479200.0,
      "text": "Adding the change in cash to the cash"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 479200.0,
      "end_time": 481600.0,
      "text": "from the start of the year, we get an ending cash balance"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 481600.0,
      "end_time": 483790.0,
      "text": "of 84,500."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 483790.0,
      "end_time": 487570.0,
      "text": "What does this tie into from the other financial statements?"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 487570.0,
      "end_time": 490000.0,
      "text": "This is the cash balance on the balance sheet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 490000.0,
      "end_time": 492430.0,
      "text": "under current assets for the current year."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 492430.0,
      "end_time": 494080.0,
      "text": "We can clearly see the interconnection"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 494080.0,
      "end_time": 497310.0,
      "text": "between the balance sheet and the statement of cash flows."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 497310.0,
      "end_time": 500040.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take a quick look at the statement of cash flows again."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 500040.0,
      "end_time": 502170.0,
      "text": "Remember, we start with the appropriate headings"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 502170.0,
      "end_time": 504240.0,
      "text": "and net income from the income statement."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 504240.0,
      "end_time": 506400.0,
      "text": "We move on to the operating activities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 506400.0,
      "end_time": 509190.0,
      "text": "than the investing activities, with the financing activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 509190.0,
      "end_time": 510510.0,
      "text": "listed last."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 510510.0,
      "end_time": 513600.0,
      "text": "The net change in cash is then added, net increase,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 513600.0,
      "end_time": 516240.0,
      "text": "as demonstrated here, or deducted"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 516240.0,
      "end_time": 519809.0,
      "text": "if it is a net decrease, from the opening cash balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 519808.99999999994,
      "end_time": 521428.99999999994,
      "text": "This will obtain the closing cash"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 521429.0,
      "end_time": 525060.0,
      "text": "balance, which is on the balance sheet under current assets."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 525060.0,
      "end_time": 526897.0,
      "text": "Now, let&#39;s quickly see the structure"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 526897.0,
      "end_time": 528480.0,
      "text": "of the statement of cash flows when we"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 528480.0,
      "end_time": 531190.0,
      "text": "use the direct method instead."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 531190.0,
      "end_time": 533470.0,
      "text": "Noticed that the operating activities do not"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 533470.0,
      "end_time": 536386.0,
      "text": "include net income or any reconciling items."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 536386.0,
      "end_time": 537760.0,
      "text": "Instead, the information provided"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 537760.0,
      "end_time": 541480.0,
      "text": "us focuses on where cash was received or paid."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 541480.0,
      "end_time": 544510.0,
      "text": "This provides better information for stakeholders to analyze"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 544510.0,
      "end_time": 546790.0,
      "text": "and, for that reason, is preferred"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 546790.0,
      "end_time": 549560.0,
      "text": "by ASPE, although not required."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 549560.0,
      "end_time": 552100.0,
      "text": "Remember that 98% of all companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 552100.0,
      "end_time": 554360.0,
      "text": "use the indirect method."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 554360.0,
      "end_time": 556600.0,
      "text": "The investing activities and the financing activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 556600.0,
      "end_time": 558460.0,
      "text": "under the direct method are exactly"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 558460.0,
      "end_time": 562160.0,
      "text": "the same as what you saw under the indirect method."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 562160.0,
      "end_time": 564060.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s check your understanding for a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 564060.0,
      "end_time": 566600.0,
      "text": "Remember to pause the video to determine your own answer"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 566600.0,
      "end_time": 568860.0,
      "text": "before continuing."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 568860.0,
      "end_time": 572730.0,
      "text": "Net income is $17,100, but the cash flow from operating"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 572730.0,
      "end_time": 575370.0,
      "text": "activities is 21,400."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 575370.0,
      "end_time": 577010.0,
      "text": "Why is there a difference?"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 582290.0,
      "end_time": 586340.0,
      "text": "The answer is not E. One of the above answers is correct."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 586340.0,
      "end_time": 589370.0,
      "text": "The answer is not D. The question specifically"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 589370.0,
      "end_time": 591380.0,
      "text": "says there is a difference between net income"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 591380.0,
      "end_time": 593150.0,
      "text": "and operating activities only."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 593150.0,
      "end_time": 595460.0,
      "text": "So this answer does not apply."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 595460.0,
      "end_time": 598490.0,
      "text": "The answer is not C. The statement of cash flows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 598490.0,
      "end_time": 601940.0,
      "text": "as its name implies, uses the cash basis of accounting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 601940.0,
      "end_time": 604010.0,
      "text": "not the accrual basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 604010.0,
      "end_time": 606440.0,
      "text": "The answer is not A. The income statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 606440.0,
      "end_time": 610730.0,
      "text": "uses the accrual basis of accounting, not the cash basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 610730.0,
      "end_time": 613610.0,
      "text": "The answer is B, because the income statement uses"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 613610.0,
      "end_time": 616070.0,
      "text": "the accrual basis of accounting, and the cash flow"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 616070.0,
      "end_time": 618896.0,
      "text": "from operation uses the cash basis of accounting."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 618896.0,
      "end_time": 620270.0,
      "text": "There will always be a difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 620270.0,
      "end_time": 623790.0,
      "text": "between net income and cash flow from operating activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 623790.0,
      "end_time": 626850.0,
      "text": "So what questions does the statement of cash answer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 626850.0,
      "end_time": 629660.0,
      "text": "For investors, it helps to determine, in conjunction"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 629660.0,
      "end_time": 631190.0,
      "text": "with the income statement, if there"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 631190.0,
      "end_time": 634280.0,
      "text": "will be enough cash in the future to pay dividends."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 634280.0,
      "end_time": 635960.0,
      "text": "For lenders and other creditors, it"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 635960.0,
      "end_time": 637940.0,
      "text": "helps determine if there is cash available"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 637940.0,
      "end_time": 640910.0,
      "text": "to pay the debts of the company as they come due."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 640910.0,
      "end_time": 643310.0,
      "text": "It also helps them determine if the company will"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 643310.0,
      "end_time": 645810.0,
      "text": "need further financing in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 645810.0,
      "end_time": 647540.0,
      "text": "Finally, all external stakeholders"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 647540.0,
      "end_time": 650060.0,
      "text": "will use the cash flow statement with the income statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 650060.0,
      "end_time": 652957.0,
      "text": "to help predict future cash flows."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 652957.0,
      "end_time": 655040.0,
      "text": "We have now completed all the financial statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 655040.0,
      "end_time": 656024.0,
      "text": "under ASPE."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 656024.0,
      "end_time": 657440.0,
      "text": "But there is an important addition"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 657440.0,
      "end_time": 658940.0,
      "text": "to the statements, which we have not"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 658940.0,
      "end_time": 661160.0,
      "text": "covered, the notes that accompany"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 661160.0,
      "end_time": 662690.0,
      "text": "the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 662690.0,
      "end_time": 666370.0,
      "text": "And that will be the topic of our next video."
    }
  ]
}